polling <- read.csv("polls_IT-parliament_2018-10-01.csv")

Purpose of this document is to show polling results in Italy.

Plotting LN

polling %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x=date,y=LN, color = "red")) + geom_point() + 
  geom_point(aes(x=date, y=M5S, color = "blue"))
